WarmUp tasks:

Task 01: ValidTriangle
         A triangle is valid if the sum of all the three angles is equal to 180 degrees.
         Write a program that declares three integers as angles
         and check whether a triangle is valid or not.

Task 02: MaximumNumber
         write a java program that accepts three numbers and return the maximum number
                (assume that none of them are equal)

Task 03: MinimumNumber
         write a java program that accepts three numbers and return the minimum number
                (assume that none of them are equal)



